Never create summary status update markdown files. These are not useful artifacts.

All go builds must be done via their associated docker-compose services.

This is the host machine, not the container. All our dependencies are installedin the containers. Use scripts/run or scrpts/docker-compose to work with services or run general commands.

eg:

scripts/docker-compose build scheduler-go
scripts/run [any shell command]
scripts/npm install
scripts/tsx [path/to/script.ts]
